<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦～<delay20 />是<tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我有一段時間沒看到你，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你是跑去其他地方了嗎～？<pageBreak /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你一定還吃了好吃的東西吧～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道你有沒有帶伴手禮之類的～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈囉～<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay frames="40" />
好久不見～！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我們好像<tag a="90" b="1" arg="0x0" />個禮拜沒見面了吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也和其他人說過，<delay20 />
最近都沒見到你～<pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay20 />你看起來很有精神，我就放心了～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大家也都很好奇你發生了什麼事，<delay20 />
記得要和大家說你回來囉～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay frames="40" /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你好像一直都不在家，<delay20 />
所以我很擔心喔～<pageBreak /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了對了，<delay20 />你不在的時候，<delay20 />
發生了一件大事喔～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你聽我說、你聽我說！<delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />是什麼事啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我下次再跟你說～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />耶～<delay20 />你終於來跟我說話了～<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為<delay20 />你好像很忙，<delay20 />
所以我不敢去找你聊天～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />終於和你說到話了～<delay frames="40" />
真是的～我們也太久沒聊天了～<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我知道<delay8 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />在這座島上，<delay20 />
但我完全找不到你啊～<pageBreak /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" />「看到我的話要和我說話！」<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你覺得<delay8 />和我做這個約定怎麼樣啊？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？<delay frames="40" />我很久<delay20 />
沒和你說話了<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />原來<delay20 />我昨天<delay20 />
是和夢裡面的你<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聊了很多事啊～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
